"attributes": {"content": "張開嘴讓我看看，啊……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（張嘴）", "name": "無名古屍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咽喉處很明顯有類似聲帶的發聲裝置，那為何到現在你都一言不發？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇怪，照理說，發聲也是聲帶與肌肉的動作，你應該能夠模仿才對啊……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "posfrom": "50,0", "posto": "80,0", "duration": 0.6}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "佩佩靠近古屍，把手搭上它的喉嚨，而古屍則依著她的樣子，將手按在佩佩的喉嚨上。"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "無名古屍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……知……道……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……滋……得……", "name": "無名古屍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "posfrom": "80,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迅速抽回手，佩佩不可思議地捂住嘴巴，眼中透出驚喜的光彩。"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的能說話啊……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太神奇了……想不到沙阿那個年代真有如此精巧的工匠技藝。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先祖曾在一本《古曆紀工藝考證》中提及......", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有異人可用源石迴路寶石封存人的意識，然後用黃金為其重塑軀殼，可供人行動千年而不腐。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長生軍……失傳的技藝……陛下會對你很有興趣的……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寶庫肯定藏在你記憶的深處。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "無名古屍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可不能僅僅是學我說話，你還得告訴我它到底在哪裡。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我看看……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“第一顆代表心臟，自它跳動，我們便存在。第二顆代表肺，當我們初次呼吸，記憶便開始。”", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“第三顆代表胃腸，食物進入肚皮，舌頭變得挑剔，我們有了喜好、個性。第四顆代表肝臟，我們清醒著進入夜晚，為了職責與義務。”", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第五顆……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第五顆是什麼？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，詩歌到這裡就斷了……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來那位阿爾薩蘭的前代研究者也沒有答案。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "無名古屍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你一定能幫我找到答案，對嗎？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1479_1#1$1", "fo