{"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）你說你不知道你現在在哪裡？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#8$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有通行證我要怎麼進去……該死，這裡的館長把辦公室搞得像保險櫃一樣。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#8$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，來不及了，現在人都快疏散完了！", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#8$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#4$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我……阿雅吉，走廊上的窗戶和館長辦公室的窗是相鄰的嗎？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#2$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是，我知道很高。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#2$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會小心的。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#2$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g7_galleriesstaircase", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一，博物館內禁止喧嘩。第二，無序乃是理性的大敵。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要推擠，這裡陳列的雕像與大型壁畫沒有展櫃保護，很容易——", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 0.4}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.4}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "120,-30", "duration": 0.4}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 25.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "120,-30", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像我剛剛說的一樣，這尊雕像差點就摔碎了，這很不好。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "150,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歷史雖然已經過去，但絕不是與我們無關，可能我們摔碎的，是五百年前的人們征服山峰的歡呼，或他們高舉葡萄酒杯的笑聲。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，您解說得真好……", "name": "迷路的遊客"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……但您確定要一直扛著這個雕像嗎？還有您手裡的其他東西？", "name": "迷路的遊客"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我要把它們帶回它們該在的地方。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都要閉館了，您真敬業。", "name": "迷路的遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……閉館？ ", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#3$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，廣播突然說有什麼緊急事件，嚇死人了！", "name": "迷路的遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#3$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個帶我們離開的糊塗蛋員工一路上左右不分，嘴上說左轉，結果把我們往右邊帶，左轉的時候，她又喊著接下來往右邊走。", "name": "迷路的遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#3$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一點我認同，女士，我也對這座博物館在某些方面的處置略有不滿。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個員工莫名其妙把我們帶到這個鬼地方來，自己又跑得無影無蹤。", "name": "迷路的遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一點我不認同，女士，容我申辯，這裡並不是鬼地方，而是米諾——", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不知道，發現迷路的時候，我們都嚇壞了。", "name": "迷路的遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是沒來得及離場，被關在博物館裡面，肯定只能見到兇神惡煞的亡魂啊！", "name": "迷路的遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看那將領的盔甲，看那活祭的祭壇……", "name": "迷路的遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對……！這就是為什麼我一直不敢來博物館……", "name": "虛弱的遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.4, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遊客的後腦勺即將撞到地板的一瞬間，阿斯帕齊婭拉住了他。"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雕像、陶罐與金杯都被暫時放下，與伊比利亞人開拓玻利瓦爾省商道所用的火炮並排。"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寶貝！你怎麼了？！", "name": "迷路的遊客"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,-100", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……應該是受到過度驚嚇導致的暈厥。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這裡有嗅鹽，能夠救急，但出去之後需要及時去醫院檢查。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯帕齊婭熟練地壓碎裹在棉花中的薄玻璃管，將濕潤的棉球湊近遊客的鼻子。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨後，她扛起甦醒的遊客，平靜地走到隊伍最前面。"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發生了緊急事件，是嗎？", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐……你的手臂好有力。", "name": "虛弱的遊客"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家跟好我，出了事情，我會保護好你們。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐……好棒。", "name": "虛弱的遊客"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g5_museum", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，小傢伙，以後不要亂跑了好嗎？", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有印象，你是拉恕爾養的寵物——", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——哎喲，你怎麼抓我！我可是剛從人潮裡把你解救出來，讓我抱一下不好嗎？", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#6$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的毛真軟，拉恕爾到底是怎麼把你弄到手的？我之前也想要一隻這麼特別的，但他死活不肯告訴我你是什麼品種，去哪裡能買到。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一開始還不明白自己為什麼這麼喜歡你，最近才恍然大悟，你長得特別像暗闌時代的雲獸雕像。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正好，現在工作人員都安排好了，遊客正在撤離，既然不能讓你亂竄，我帶你去我的工作室看看正在修復的那尊雕像吧。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g13_smallroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越過層層向下的階梯，梅捷緹克緹來到了用於文物修復的房間。"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了減少對文物的影響，空調溫度很低，空氣又冷又乾。巨大的房間內只有一盞白熾燈照明，她吐了一口氣，發現竟然能夠凝成白霧。"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "平時協助修復的員工都被派去維持館內秩序了，地下層一片死寂。抽抽鼻子，她覺得心跳得有些快。"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要怕，小傢伙，我的工作台就在這裡……", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#9$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桌台上還殘留著一些類似樹脂的金色物質，那是緹緹使用源石技藝輔助修復文物的痕跡。"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但原本放在桌上的雲獸雕像卻不見蹤影。"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1484_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g6_museum_core", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，我沒看到雲獸……", "name": "閒逛的員工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1484_1#1$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$flashback"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1486_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g1_menatmainstreet_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛，在你的額頭有一片陰影掠過，這不是什麼好徵兆，它預告著你會遭遇厄運。", "name": "異鄉的遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1486_1#5$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1482_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "49_g13_smallroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "100,0", "duration": 0.9}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……你到底是什麼？", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#8$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你難道也復活了？和那具古屍一樣？！", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#5$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 50.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊啊啊！我辛辛苦苦把你修好，不是為了讓你和阿娜特的研究對象一樣亂跑！", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更不是為了給自己招來厄運！", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "發生什麼了？！！誰在尖叫！", "name": "倉庫保管員"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦……梅捷緹克緹女士，您、您怎麼在這裡？", "name": "倉庫保管員"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛接到要暫時閉館的通知，以為您短時間裡不會回來了，所以幫您把修復中的文物收起來了……", "name": "倉庫保管員"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個……", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#5$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沒什麼，我今天想加班了，你先走吧。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1478_1#2$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g4_ctizengarden", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$sjoyasorrow_intro", "key": "$sjoyasorrow_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_020", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1", "duration": 0.8}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？從東南展廳疏散的那一批遊客還沒找到？不是說叫吉雅阿帶出來了嗎？", "name": "博物館保全"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我得關門了！是副館長親自發布的緊急閉館指令，我都不敢想像事情有多糟糕！", "name": "博物館保全"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有人去裡面找過了嗎？", "name": "博物館售票員"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經派人去了，但都說找不到，吉雅阿到底把人帶去哪裡……", "name": "博物館保全"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "博物館保全"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼突然不說話了？", "name": "博物館售票員"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽……", "name": "博物館保全"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽什麼？", "name": "博物館售票員"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是風的聲音。", "name": "博物館保全"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陽光下，一列隊伍緩緩走出了大門。"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$comedy_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為首的女人神色專注寧靜，幾十人的隊伍井然有序，跟隨在她後面。"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風帶起她的衣角，吹亂她的髮絲，她毫無動搖地扛著肩上虛弱的遊客，猶如一尊屹立多年的雕像被賦予生命。"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_020", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我總覺得這個場景在哪裡見過……", "name": "博物館保全"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我明白，我看過那尊雕像很多次。", "name": "博物館售票員"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有這種姿勢的雕像？", "name": "博物館保全"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，謝天謝地，終於可以關門了。", "name": "博物館保全"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太感謝了，這是我的名片，您如果有空照顧我們家族的寶石生意，我一定為您提供最高等級貴賓服務。", "name": "迷路的遊客"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，你到時候來炎國玩啊！阿姨家裡還有個兒子，長得可帥了。我姐家還有個單身的女兒，剛去天師府上班，你也可以見見。", "name": "熱情的遊客"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝各位，不必……我只是做了我該做的事情……", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#8$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rollingdoor", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#4$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯帕齊婭猛地回過頭。"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐵捲門緩緩放下，保全人員正在將“今日閉館”的牌子拖到大門前面。"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我的金杯呢？我的陶罐呢？我的雕像呢？", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#3$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g10_grandbazaar_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.5, "channel": "2", "delay": 0.15}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_804_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1258_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜娜到底跑哪裡去了？都這個時候了。", "name": "風姿綽約的女人"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "石榴石漿果店裡沒有，琉璃琺瑯瓷器店裡沒有，就連她最愛鑽的天青石貼片水管裡也沒有……", "name": "風姿綽約的女人"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，找了這麼久，簡直是浪費時間。我看，那隻雲獸就是被博物館暴走的古屍吃掉了。", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "討厭，怎麼會！", "name": "風姿綽約的女人"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_804_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寵物，寵一時就算了，好東西多的是，你想要什麼，我都買給你！", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你點頭，別說那些名貴寶石了，就連整個寶石交易所，我也能買下來送給你！", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（抬起頭）", "name": "神祕的動物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_804_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1258_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "風姿綽約的女人"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_804_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？你這是默許了？", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，你看你腳邊……", "name": "風姿綽約的女人"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（瞪）", "name": "神祕的動物"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_804_1#10$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1258_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……怎麼是拉恕爾養的崽子。", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_804_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，裝什麼威風？", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "冷傲的市民"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_804_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1258_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……咳咳，你在啊，拉恕爾。", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正好，我們做個買賣吧，我的姑娘對這間寶石交易所很感興趣。", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別鬧了，我可沒這麼說……", "name": "風姿綽約的女人"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在薩爾貢東部有一座移動平台，建有規模龐大的源石精煉廠、染料廠、糧食加工廠……", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把所有這些都加起來，再附贈些金銀財寶，夠買下這間寶石交易所了吧？", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我拒絕。", "name": "拉恕爾"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你承擔不起這間寶石交易所的重量。", "name": "拉恕爾"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_804_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，重量……小夥子，你倒是繼承了你外祖父的高傲。", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽我一句勸吧，要嘛像他一樣，養幾頭兇惡的裂獸來鎮場子。", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要嘛讓你的小雲獸來迎接像我這樣的貴客，至少牠還會賣賣乖……", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_angrydog"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-100,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_804_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶——好痛！你這畜生，你咬我？", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_804_1#4$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_angrydog"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（呲牙）", "name": "神祕的動物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dogbarknormal"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "汪——！", "name": "神祕的動物"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1483_1#1$1"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_804_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "-100,0", "posto": "-300,0", "duration": 0.8, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，滾開啊，別追——別追上來啊——！", "name": "穿金戴玉的男人"}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dogbarkangry"}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "汪汪汪——！", "name": "神祕的動物"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沃奧，別生氣了。", "name": "拉恕爾"}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不懷敬意的人已經跑遠了。", "name": "拉恕爾"}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_dogbarknormal"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "汪嗷！", "name": "沃奧"}}, {"id": 465, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？想要讓我摸摸？……這裡嗎？", "name": "拉恕爾"}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（開心地舔舔）", "name": "沃奧"}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wing"}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一隻羽獸飛來，停落在年輕的寶石交易所監管人的肩頭。"}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "監管人撥弄了金屬羽獸身上的幾處機關，隨後上緊發條，將羽獸重新放飛。"}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 475, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……他越來越活躍了。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#8$1"}, {"id": 476, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 477, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們想必也很期待和他見面吧？米奧很少這麼積極地外出。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#8$1"}, {"id": 478, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才那人說要讓小雲獸來迎接重要的客人，或許也有道理。", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#8$1"}, {"id": 479, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4140_lasher_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 480, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……米奧真的能把他吸引過來嗎？", "name": "拉恕爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4140_lasher_1#8$1"}, {"id": 481, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 482, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 483, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 484, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 485, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 486, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 487, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 488, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}